 <title>Timeout to Close Idle Files</title>
 <conbody>
  <p><indexterm>MapR FS destination<indexterm>idle timeout</indexterm></indexterm><indexterm>idle
                    timeout<indexterm>MapR FS</indexterm></indexterm>You can configure the maximum
            time that an open output file can remain idle. After no records are written to an output
            file for the specified amount of time, the MapR FS destination closes the file. </p>
